OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FVoters will head to the polls next
OL,7,Fmonth in the first by-election to be
OL,8,Fheld since Reform UK took control of
OL,9,FKent County Council.
OL,11,FThe by-election for Cliftonville has
OL,12,Fbeen set for 9 April, the local
OL,13,Fauthority has confirmed.
OL,15,FIt comes as ex-Reform UK councillor
OL,16,FDaniel Taylor, of Ramsgate, Kent, was
OL,17,Fjailed for 12 months last month after
OL,18,Fadmitting controlling and coercive
OL,19,Fbehaviour towards his wife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
