OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FThe 36-year-old was suspended from
OL,7,FReform after his arrest in June last
OL,8,Fyear and expelled after he pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to the crime in January.
OL,11,FReform won control of Kent County
OL,12,FCouncil (KCC) in May last year,
OL,13,Fsecuring 57 out of 81 seats, but is
OL,14,Fcurrently down to 47 after removing
OL,15,Fsome of them.
OL,17,FIn the Cliftonville seat, the party
OL,18,Fwon 40% of the vote, followed by
OL,19,FLabour and the Conservatives behind
OL,20,Fthem with 22% and 20% of the vote
OL,21,Frespectively.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
