OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "The
OL,7,Fpeople of Cliftonville deserve a
OL,8,Fstrong Reform UK councillor to
OL,9,Frepresent them in Kent County Council.
OL,10,FWe look forward to announcing our
OL,11,Fcandidate in due course."
OL,13,FIt comes as seven former Reform
OL,14,Fcouncillors have joined Rupert Lowe's
OL,15,Fnew political party Restore Britain
OL,16,Fand created a new group at Kent County
OL,17,FCouncil last month.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
