OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FChallengers for the by-election
OL,7,Falready announced include Rob Yates
OL,8,Ffor the Green Party, Dr Mo Shafaei for
OL,9,Fthe Liberal Democrats and Charlie Leys
OL,10,Ffor the Conservatives.
OL,12,FEndorsing Mr Leys, former South Thanet
OL,13,FMP and now Lord Craig Mackinlay
OL,14,Fappealed to Tory voters who were
OL,15,F"seduced by the Reform message" to
OL,16,F"come back home".
OL,18,FThe Conservative peer added that the
OL,19,Fward returned a Reform councillor and
OL,20,F"that's gone horribly wrong and that's
OL,21,Fwhy we've got a by-election".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
