OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FKCC's Conservative group leader Harry
OL,7,FRayner said the party is already
OL,8,Fcampaigning and it is going to be a
OL,9,F"really interesting" by-election given
OL,10,Fhow the outgoing councillor lost his
OL,11,Fseat.
OL,13,FThe local authority's leader of the
OL,14,Fopposition and Liberal Democrats group
OL,15,Fleader Antony Hook said people in
OL,16,FCliftonville "deserve better" than
OL,17,Fthey had under Reform, adding: "Lib
OL,18,FDem Dr Shafaei will be the local
OL,19,Fchampion people need."
