OL,3,CKent County Council by-election to be
OL,4,Cheld next month after councillor jailed
OL,6,FLabour will be launching its campaign
OL,7,Fand revealing its candidate on
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,FLabour KCC group leader Alister Brady
OL,11,Fsaid: "We will have a candidate who is
OL,12,Fa local champion ` who already does a
OL,13,Flot to better the community they call
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,F"So much trust has been lost because
OL,17,Fof the previous Reform councillor and
OL,18,Fthis must be regained so Cliftonville
OL,19,Fresidents can be given the support
OL,20,Fthey deserve and need."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
